meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 10 , 11 , 12 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q1' WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 1 , 2 , 3 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q2' WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 4 , 5 , 6 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q3' WHEN MONTH ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) IN ( 7 , 8 , 9 ) THEN YEAR ( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q4' ELSE NULL END AS "Timeframe" FORMAT "%Y-%m"

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" ) = 0 AND "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" IN ( 'B' ) THEN "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" || ' - Automatic' WHEN ISNULL ( "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" ) = 0 AND "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" NOT IN ( 'B' ) THEN "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" || ' - Manual' WHEN ISNULL ( "_CEL_O2C_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" ) = 1 THEN 'unknown' END AS "User Type"

axis0.name: User Type
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 0 AND "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" IN (<%= AutoTypes %>) 
        THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" || ' - Automatic'
    WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 0 AND "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" NOT IN (<%= AutoTypes %>) 
        THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" || ' - Manual'
    WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 1 
        THEN 'unknown'
END

axis2.name: # Automation (Unknown)
axis2.text:
SUM( CASE 
    WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 1
    OR  (ISNULL("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 0
    AND  "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  NOT IN (<%= AutoActivities %>))
    THEN 1 ELSE NULL 
END )

components.message:
General Information

#{This Sheet provides information about the degree of automation of the process. }

KPI Definition

#{# Activities (Selected): }
#{Number of selected activities (user defined) that are potentially automated. The selected activities are split into automated, manual and unknown activities.}

#{# Activities (Automated): }
#{Number of selected activities (user defined) that are completed automatically (by a batch system user).}

#{# Activities (Manual): }
#{Number of selected activities (user defined) that are completed manually (by a user).}

#{# Unknown Activities: }
#{Number of selected activities (user defined) where the executer is unknown.}

#{Automation Rate: }
#{Share of automated activities. Calculated as # Activities (Automated) divided by # Activities (Automated) plus # Activities (Manual).}

Further Resources

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (10,11,12) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || ' - Q1'
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (1,2,3) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || ' - Q2'
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (4,5,6) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) || ' - Q3'
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") IN (7,8,9) THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || ' - Q4'
ELSE NULL
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") ||'-' || MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT")
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") ||'-0' || MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT")
--- ADD one Year if we are already in CW 1 at the end of December
+ CASE WHEN MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT") = 12 AND CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT") = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
|| '-CW-' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT")
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT") || '-CW-0' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("VBAK"."ERDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH( "VBAK"."ERDAT" ) >= 10
THEN CASE
WHEN DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
END
ELSE CASE
WHEN DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("VBAK"."ERDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("VBAK"."ERDAT" )
END
END

variables.title: ButtonDrilldown3
variables.variableValue: CASE WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 THEN 'a) 0 - 100€' WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 THEN 'b) 100 - 500€' WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1000 THEN 'c) 500 - 1.000€' WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1000 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 THEN 'd) 1.000 - 10.000€' ELSE 'e) > 10.000€' END
